Subject: rogue leaving terminal in wrong mode
Index: games/rogue 2.9BSD

Description:
	Upon saving a game in rogue (under 2.9BSD) the user is left
in the mode stty -echo nl.  At various times the user is locked into
upper case as well.

Repeat-By:
	Saving a rogue game on a small PDP-11 (ll/24 ll/23)

